text: Segun Owobowale (born 17 August 1997) is a Dutch football attacking midfielder who is a free agent. ==Club career== Owobowale is a youth exponent from ADO Den Haag. He made his Eredivisie debut on 30 August 2014 in a 3–2 away defeat against SC Cambuur. ==International career== Owobowale was born in the Netherlands to a Nigerian father and a Dutch mother.
